{"tid":10672,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"索泳照！35歲大肚葉翠翠逼爆C cup胸","createTime":"2016-11-29T04:42:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T07:00:10.000Z","uid":22869,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9b9b8944b39f0531d1cf3ba5f9c45050d3e72a38","tid":10672,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T04:42:25.000Z","msg":"【尖肚似陀仔？】索泳照！35歲大肚葉翠翠逼爆C cup胸<br />\n<br />\n現年35歲嘅葉翠翠去年7月嫁畀拍拖僅十個月、任建築公司副董事金，婚後全力造人的翠翠，早前宣佈造人成功，將喺明年添「雞丁」，預產期喺老公生日前，每次做產檢，老公都堅持同行，翠翠講過「中醫已經畀咗貼士我哋，老公好開心，話BB一定要似佢」，咁即係暗示呢胎生男B噃!?<br />\n<br />\n翠翠今日喺網上貼出性感三點式相，留言：「肚子大了不少，就算旅行也不可以懶惰，每天做適量運動，對BB是十分有幫助，也因為懷孕後吃太多東西了，做些運動對身體也有益處。在這裡定了目標，每天游泳兩次，當然要避開猛烈太陽的時候。」<br />\n相見身穿粉紅色三點式嘅翠翠，大晒白滑皮膚，目測佢由選港姐嗰陣擁有32A上圍，升到C cup罩杯，大肚婆都要注重健康去游水，睇佢個肚亦比較尖。民間流傳「尖肚」係陀仔!  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/29/124125_e2cc4dac7d9a18e6635d244936ea72c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F124125_e2cc4dac7d9a18e6635d244936ea72c1.jpg&h=36ab2b1d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/29/124127_7cd0d1c1c4f995e87bc841402ef7a1fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F124127_7cd0d1c1c4f995e87bc841402ef7a1fc.jpg&h=3cb6d872&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/006RCZS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F006RCZS.jpg&h=6b8f692c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20161127/55972267\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20161127%2F55972267&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=d4bb1b42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20161127%2F55972267&h=e0700f44\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20161127/55972267</a>"},{"pid":"3b209